name: agdelte-auth
include: .
depend:
  standard-library
  agdelte
-- Generic security library (extracted from the agdelte framework): JWT, signed URLs,
-- role checks, HTTP auth middleware, and an auth client. Depends DOWN only on the
-- agdelte framework (FFI.Crypto/Server/Time/Json, Core.Cmd). Domain-neutral — sits
-- above the framework; consumed by domain libs (courses now; CRM when authz lands).
-- Module names kept `Agdelte.Auth.*` so consumers' imports don't change.
